Add MeanFlow single-step inference support
Features: - Implement sample_one_step method in MeanFlowScheduler for single-step generation - Modify WanPipeline to support MeanFlow single-step inference when num_inference_steps=1 - Update test configuration to use MeanFlow scheduler with single-step inference - Add support for MeanFlow test scheduler in WanTrainer - Enable both training (dual-timestep) and inference (single-step) capabilities

- Integrate MeanFlow scheduler with JVP-based training - Add configurable dual timestep sampling (v0/v1 strategies) - Support adaptive weighting and logit-normal distribution - Enable MeanFlow in training configuration - Maintain backward compatibility with original FlowMatchEulerDiscreteScheduler
